From 19d5bc114cf4440f54d65f9b1c7f35a3513eb332 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alessio Ferri <alessio.ferri@mythread.it>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 08:26:50 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/9] b43: AC-PHY register definitions and table accessors

Add the PHY register defines, struct b43_phy_ac fields (num_cores,
coremask), channel table structures, and the table read/write helpers
for 16/32-bit AC-PHY tables (including the r11 alternate data register
path and the table-write gate lock/unlock).

New files: tables_phy_ac.c, tables_phy_ac.h.

Signed-off-by: Alessio Ferri <alessio.ferri@mythread.it>
